text:
Needed antibiotics for my mum's Uti condition
As my mum was staying in the home
I had to rush from the home (after work) to get the prescription and pass it to unity pharmacy.
Plus next day was a Public Holiday!
Ms Lim was very helpful and even waited for me even though she finishes work 730pm

Thank you Ms Lim!
Friendly staffs and pharmacy. Pharmacy is quick at dispensing medication. Comes here quite often

Got a great help here from the service staff today 10.30am 24Apr Monday.

I had wanted to buy one mask for my hospital visit and was assisted greatly by the staff here.

Appreciate it very much. Cheers
Not a wide variety of toiletries and supplements. The lady pharmacist there is not helpful when customer asks questions about some medication.
Staff is Beyond rude. Called at 10.17am on 26 Apr to ask for stock availability. Staff just brushed me off and said call back later then hang up on me. Might as well not pick up the call?
